import {Link} from 'react-router-dom';

export default function Menu (props){
    
<details>
<summary></summary>
<nav class="menu">
  <Link to='/about'>
        <button>About</button>
        </Link>
        
        <Link to='/home'>
        <button>Home</button>
        </Link>

        <Link to='/favorites'>
        <button>Favorites</button>
        </Link>


        <button onClick={props.logOut}>LogOut</button>
  </nav>
</details>
}
